Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20with%20a%20keyboard%20in%20the%20background%20shown%20playing%20a%20game%20based%20on%20naval%20warfare%20on%20the%20display.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c22a68b8b41a9673f9600b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20benchmarks%20like%20the%20iPhone%2015%20for%20gaming%20performance%2C%20but%20it%20runs%20AAA%20games%20and%20supports%20ray%20tracing.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGaming-wise%2C%20performance%20is%20largely%20similar%20to%20the%20iPhone%2016%2C%20with%20support%20for%20ray%20tracing%20and%20demanding%20AAA%20titles%20despite%20the%20missing%20GPU%20core.%20In%20benchmark%20tests%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20scores%20almost%20identically%20to%20the%20iPhone%2015%20running%20on%20the%20A16%20processor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261d01b6b-3e3c-4f7d-9406-c212182a97c2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Apple%20Intelligence%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20Intelligence%3A%20The%20cheapest%20phone%20with%20Apple's%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20A18%20processor%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20supports%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%2C%20which%20plays%20a%20large%20role%20in%20Apple's%20value%20proposition%20for%20the%20iPhone%2016e.%20It's%20a%20notable%20upgrade%20over%20the%20iPhone%2015%20and%20iPhone%2014%2C%20which%20are%20incompatible%20with%20the%20AI%20suite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20on%20a%20wooden%20surface%20shown%20using%20ChatGPT%20processing%20a%20request.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c229e5b1834fe31165dae3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChatGPT%20is%20used%20throughout%20the%20Apple%20Intelligence%20experience%2C%20including%20with%20Siri%20and%20Writing%20Tools.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dissect%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20more%20fully%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fiphone-16-review%23apple-intelligence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%2016%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20in%20summary%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20distinguishing%20feature%20is%20Siri's%20integration%20with%20the%20ChatGPT%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20which%20essentially%20makes%20Siri%20much%20more%20useful%20and%20able%20to%20process%20significantly%20complex%20tasks.%20You%20can%20get%20help%20devising%20a%20workout%20plan%20or%20plan%20an%20entire%20trip%2C%20among%20many%20other%20things.%20It's%20like%20it%20does%20the%20research%20for%20you%2C%20or%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20good%20starting%20point%20for%20daunting%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20like%20most%20about%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20chatbots%20is%20they%20give%20me%20a%20straight%20answer%20rather%20than%20offering%20a%20list%20of%20links%20to%20sift%20through%20myself%2C%20as%20previous%20AI%20assistants%20have.%20Just%20be%20aware%20that%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20chatbots%20can%20occasionally%20return%20with%20outdated%20and%20incorrect%20information%2C%20so%20it's%20best%20to%20double-check%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20answer%20seems%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20on%20a%20wooden%20surface%20shown%20processing%20a%20prompt%20to%20create%20an%20AI-generated%20email%2C%20and%20another%20image%20showing%20the%20result.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c22a24b1834fe31165daed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWriting%20Tools%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20relieve%20you%20of%20ever%20writing%20an%20email%20again.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20headlining%20feature%20in%20Apple%20Intelligence%20is%20Writing%20Tools%2C%20which%20can%20be%20immensely%20useful.%20You%20can%20write%20entire%20emails%20with%20various%20tones%20based%20on%20short%20prompts%2C%20and%20it's%20excellent%20for%20summarizing%20longer%20emails.%20Shorthand%20notes%20in%20the%20Notes%20app%20can%20also%20be%20converted%20into%20full%20prose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20shown%20running%20Apple's%20Visual%20Intelligence%20feature%20providing%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20care%20for%20an%20orchid%20that%20it's%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c22abdb1834fe31165db18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVIsual%20Intelligence%20lets%20you%20point%20the%20camera%20to%20whatever%20sparks%20your%20curiosity%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20it.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVisual%20Intelligence%20lets%20you%20use%20your%20camera%20to%20identify%20and%20get%20more%20information%20on%20an%20object%2C%20like%20an%20unfamiliar%20plant.%20You%20can%20then%20ask%20more%20specific%20questions%2C%20like%20how%20to%20care%20for%20said%20plant.%20It%20works%20well%20and%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20your%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Photos%20app%2C%20Apple%20Intelligence%20powers%20the%20Cleanup%20feature%2C%20which%20removes%20unwanted%20objects%20from%20a%20picture.%20It%20works%20well%20for%20smaller%20details%20but%20struggles%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20details%20behind%20larger%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmaller%20Apple%20Intelligence%20features%20include%20Genmoji%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20create%20an%20emoji%20of%20your%20own%20if%20the%20one%20you're%20looking%20for%20doesn't%20exist.%20It's%20a%20great%20tool%20for%20creating%20simpler%20emojis%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20master%20writing%20prompts%20for%20more%20complex%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Playground%20app%20lets%20you%20create%20images%20of%20almost%20anything%20based%20on%20prompts%2C%20and%20I%20struggle%20to%20find%20any%20good%20use%20for%20it.%20One%20example%20is%20creating%20an%20image%20for%20an%20invitation%20in%20the%20Apple%20Invites%20app.%20However%2C%20AI-generated%20images%20have%20a%20certain%20and%20identifiable%20look%20to%20them%2C%20and%20I%20find%20them%20off-putting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Apple%20Intelligence%20can%20be%20useful%2C%20and%20it's%20continually%20improving%20and%20expanding.%20The%20greatest%20hurdle%20with%20the%20evolving%20AI%20suite%20is%20knowing%20which%20features%20are%20available%20and%20how%20they%20can%20be%20applied%20to%20whatever%20you%20do%20on%20your%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b2159df-3bc9-45ec-b4c1-a8f68e4148ba%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Display%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisplay%3A%20On%20par%20with%20previous%20flagship%20models%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20on%20a%20wooden%20surface%20showing%20its%20display%20with%20the%20home%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c22b4b69253ccddf97f8f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e's%20display%20looks%20great%20in%202025%20(for%20%24600)%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20from%20a%202022%20iPhone.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e's%20display%20is%20identical%20to%20the%20iPhone%2014's%2C%20which%20means%20it's%20a%206.1-inch%20Super%20Retina%20XDR%20OLED%20panel%20with%20a%2060Hz%20refresh%20rate%2C%20up%20to%201%2C200%20nits%20brightness%2C%20and%20Apple's%20previous-generation%20Ceramic%20Shield%20glass.%20It's%20also%20a%20substantial%20improvement%20over%20the%202022%20iPhone%20SE's%204.7-inch%20Retina%20HD%20LCD%20display%2C%20which%20was%20only%20capable%20of%20625%20nits%20brightness%20and%20a%20lower%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e's%20display%20effectively%20provides%20an%20experience%20on%20par%20with%20the%20iPhone%2015%20and%2016.%20Despite%20lower%20maximum%20brightness%2C%20it%20looks%20as%20bright%20in%20direct%20sunlight%20as%20the%20last%20two%20flagship%20models.%20It%20doesn't%20go%20as%20low%20as%20one%20nit%2C%20as%20the%20iPhone%2016's%20display%20can%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20comfortable%20to%20use%20in%20the%20dark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20Plus%20version%20of%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20with%20a%20larger%20display%2C%20like%20the%206.7-inch%20iPhone%2016%20Plus.%20That's%20a%20shame%2C%20as%20the%20%24800%20iPhone%2015%20Plus%20is%20now%20the%20least%20expensive%20iPhone%20option%20with%20a%20big%20display%2C%20whereas%20the%20iPhone%2014%20Plus%20recently%20sold%20for%20%24100%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20hardwearing%20than%20the%20latest-generation%20Ceramic%20Shield%20glass%20of%20the%20iPhone%2016%20models%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20original%20Ceramic%20Shield%20screen%20is%20comparatively%20susceptible%20to%20damage.%20See%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-iphone-16e-screen-protectors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20iPhone%2016e%20screen%20protectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20preserve%20the%20phone's%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a99f937-7bf6-427f-b861-2177a5dfa8e1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%225G%20connectivity%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5G%20connectivity%3A%20No%20super-fast%205G%2C%20but%20you%20might%20not%20notice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20supports%20the%20low-%20and%20mid-band%205G%20networks%20provided%20by%20any%20carrier%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20support%20high-band%20mmWave%205G%20networks%20offered%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-cell-phone-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20cell%20phone%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Verizon%2C%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20or%20T-Mobile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20might%20not%20even%20notice%2C%20as%20low-%20and%20mid-band%205G%20networks%20are%20plenty%20fast%20for%20common%20data-heavy%20tasks%2C%20like%20streaming%20video%20or%20scrolling%20social%20media%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20works%20fine%20on%20premium%20plans%2C%20though%20it%20simply%20won't%20connect%20to%20their%20mmWave%205G%20networks.%20On%20T-Mobile's%20premium%20Go5G%20Plus%20plan%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20means%20your%20speeds%20would%20be%20limited%20to%20around%20350%20megabits-per-second%20instead%20of%20around%20400.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20350Mbps%20is%20more%20than%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20I%20have%20a%20300Mbps%20internet%20connection%20at%20home%2C%20and%20I%20stream%20home%20monitoring%20cameras%2C%20YouTube%2C%204K%20videos%2C%20and%20browse%20the%20web%20simultaneously%20without%20any%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReally%2C%20the%20only%20issue%20in%20using%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20with%20a%20premium%20plan%20is%20that%20you%20might%20be%20overpaying%20for%20mmWave%205G%20access%2C%20which%20the%20phone%20can't%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20then%2C%20you%20can%20still%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20prioritized%20data%20that%20premium%20plans%20usually%20include.%20Prioritized%20data%20means%20your%20speeds%20won't%20be%20artificially%20throttled%20when%20the%20network%20is%20congested%2C%20and%20you'll%20always%20get%20the%20fastest%20low-%20and%20mid-band%205G%20and%20LTE%20data%20available%20in%20your%20coverage%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20considering%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20value-driven%20price%20and%20lack%20of%20mmWave%205G%20support%2C%20it's%20ideally%20paired%20with%20a%20value-driven%20carrier%20or%20mobile%20virtual%20network%20operator%20(MVNO)%2C%20like%20those%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-cheap-cell-phone-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20cheap%20cell%20phone%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20plan%20options%20from%20MVNOs%20like%20Mint%20Mobile%2C%20Visible%2C%20Tello%2C%20and%20US%20Mobile%20don't%20include%20high-band%205G%20network%20access%2C%20so%20you're%20not%20paying%20for%20mmWave%205G%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22015e3ced-3fbe-49b3-ae80-03d2585babf3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cameras%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECameras%3A%20Ditching%20ultrawide%2C%20but%20doubling%20down%20on%20zoom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20sports%20a%20single%2048MP%20rear%20camera%20that%20takes%20excellent%20photos%20for%20its%20%24600%20price%20tag%20with%20balanced%20brightness%2C%20contrast%2C%20and%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20the%20Oculus%20and%20a%20colorful%20art%20installment%20taken%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0de64b1834fe31165bb9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20delivers%20Apple's%20signature%20reliability%20for%20taking%20high-quality%20photos.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20colorful%20art%20installment%20in%20New%20York%20City%20taken%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0e1a6b1834fe31165bc6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20takes%20balanced%20photos%20that%20don't%20try%20too%20hard%20to%20boost%20the%20photo's%20appearance%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20social%20media.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20default%2C%20photos%20are%20snapped%20at%2024MP%2C%20but%20all%2048MP%20are%20used%20in%20a%20process%20called%20pixel%20binning.%20This%20process%20essentially%20combines%20all%20the%20small%20pixels%20to%20create%20larger%20pixels%20that%20absorb%20more%20light%2C%20leading%20to%20clearer%20photos%20under%20any%20lighting%20condition%2C%20whether%20bright%20or%20dark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20Grand%20Central%20Terminal%20taken%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0dd4bb8b41a9673f9405f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELow-light%20photos%20look%20fine%20when%20flicking%20through%20them%2C%20but%20they're%20notably%20less%20sharp%20than%20the%20iPhone%2016's%20if%20you're%20pixel%20peeping.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20taken%20in%20low-light%20conditions%20look%20great%20on%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20display%2C%20but%20they%20become%20slightly%20less%20sharp%20compared%20to%20the%20iPhone%2016's%20low-light%20photos%20when%20viewed%20on%20a%20larger%20computer%20monitor.%20Still%2C%20most%20people%20will%20be%20pleased%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20low-light%20camera%20performance%2C%20considering%20its%20lower%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20oh%20the%20Oculus%20in%20New%20York%20City%20taken%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20camera%20at%202x%20zoom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0dc5ab8b41a9673f94021%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20takes%202x%20optical-quality%20photos%2C%20which%20many%20may%20appreciate.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%