5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c0e0a5b8b41a9673f9414e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20at%206x%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20captures%20an%20impressive%20amount%20of%20detail%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20using%20digital%20zooming%20at%20that%20range.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20unfortunate%20trade-off%20for%20those%20who%20value%20taking%20ultrawide%20photos.%20However%2C%20while%20I%20sometimes%20wished%20I%20had%20an%20ultrawide%20camera%20to%20capture%20more%20of%20a%20scene%2C%20the%201x%20photos%20I%20took%20looked%20better%20than%20anticipated.%20It%20made%20me%20question%20whether%20I%20should%20use%20my%20phone's%20ultrawide%20camera%20as%20much%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20camera%20is%20less%20versatile%20than%20the%20two-camera%20system%20of%20the%20iPhone%2014%2C%20the%20phone%20it%20replaced%20as%20Apple's%20%24600%20option.%20With%20the%20iPhone%2014%2C%20you%20had%20the%20option%20to%20take%20zoomed%20shots%20with%20its%2012MP%20camera.%20With%20a%201x%20optical%20zoom%2C%20its%20results%20aren't%20as%20crisp%20as%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%202x%20optical%20zoom%2C%20but%20they're%20still%20usable%20to%20an%20extent.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20doesn't%20give%20you%20the%20option%20to%20take%20ultrawide%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20video%20quality%2C%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20can%20record%20video%20up%20to%204K%20resolution%20at%2060%20frames-per-second%2C%20and%20point-and-shoot%20quality%20is%20very%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20lacks%20certain%20video%20features%2C%20like%20Cinematic%20mode%20(basically%20portrait%20mode%20for%20video)%2C%20Action%20mode%2C%20spatial%20video%20recording%20for%20playback%20on%20Apple's%20Vision%20Pro%20headset%2C%20and%20macro%20video%20recording.%20These%20are%20expected%20compromises%20for%20a%20more%20budget-minded%20iPhone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20also%20doesn't%20feature%20sensor-shift%20optical%20stabilization%2C%20available%20to%20flagship%20iPhones%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20iPhone%2013%2C%20and%20instead%20features%20basic%20optical%20stabilization.%20Videos%20from%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20are%20slightly%20more%20shaky%20than%20the%20iPhone%2016's%20while%20walking%2C%20but%20less%20so%20than%20I%20expected.%20Videos%20recorded%20while%20in%20motion%20are%20certainly%20usable%20for%20most%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dbba7aed-ede8-4fdf-987c-772d119e2ac3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%20life%20and%20charging%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20life%20and%20charging%3A%20Exceptional%20battery%2C%20but%20a%20confounding%20lack%20of%20MagSafe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e's%20bottom%20edge%20showing%20its%20USB-C%20port%2C%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20against%20a%20gravel%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c2294669253ccddf97f875%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20has%20the%20best%20battery%20life%20we've%20tested%20on%20a%206.1-inch%20phone%2C%20almost%20reaching%20the%20battery%20score%20of%20the%206.7-inch%20iPhone%2016%20Plus.%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Villas-Boas%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20Apple%20makes%20good%20on%20an%20iPhone%20battery%20claim.%20Apple's%20claim%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20has%20the%20best%20battery%20life%20in%20a%206.1-inch%20phone%20is%20true.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20ended%20our%20test%20with%2068%25%2C%20which%20is%20even%20better%20than%20the%20iPhone%2016's%2065%25%20score.%20The%20iPhone%2016%20previously%20held%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-phone-battery-life%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20phone%20battery%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20result%20for%20the%206.1-inch%20range%2C%20so%20the%20iPhone%2016e's%20score%20is%20truly%20impressive.%20To%20note%2C%20it's%20almost%20as%20good%20as%20the%206.7-inch%20iPhone%2016%20Plus'%2070%25%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20charges%20via%20USB-C%20at%20typical%20iPhone%20charging%20speeds%20(between%2020%20and%2025W)%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20support%20Apple's%20wireless%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-magsafe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMagSafe%20charging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20utterly%20mystifying.%20It%20only%20supports%20wireless%20charging%20with%20the%20Qi%20standard%2C%20which%20is%20slow%20at%20under%2010W%20compared%20to%20the%20latest%20MagSafe%20standard's%2025W.%20Even%20the%20original%20MagSafe%20standard%20with%2015W%20charging%20speeds%20would%20have%20been%20appreciated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20magnetic%20case%20for%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20can%20soften%20the%20blow%20of%20its%20lacking%20MagSafe%2C%20letting%20you%20at%20least%20place%20the%20iPhone%2016e%20on%20a%20MagSafe%20charger%20and%20use%20MagSafe%20accessories.%20Yet%2C%20wireless%20charging%20speeds%20will%20remain%20at%20Qi%20standards.%20See%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-iphone-16e-cases%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20iPhone%2016e%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20various%20top%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223cded208-429d-422a-aa30-f7bdf314017e%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20iPhone%2016e%20held%20in%20a%20hand%20against%20a%20gravel%20background%20showing%20its%20rear.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c22b7669253ccddf97f8fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20iPhone%2016e%20may%