the%20best%20dog%20muzzles%20can%20help%20keep%20you%20and%20your%20dog%20safe%20in%20various%20situations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20muzzle%20for%20dogs%20that%20eat%20everything%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20basket%20muzzle%20can%20be%20a%20good%20option%20for%20dogs%20that%20attempt%20to%20eat%20objects%20they%20aren't%20supposed%20to.%20Malawey%20advises%20purchasing%20the%20muzzle%20that%20will%20work%20best%20for%20their%20specific%20physiology%20to%20ensure%20you%20get%20a%20secure%20fit.%20A%20poorly%20fitted%20muzzle%20may%20not%20stop%20a%20dog%20from%20eating%20foreign%20objects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-muzzle%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740781371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c2323ab8b41a9673f961de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-muzzle%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20dog%20muzzles%20prevent%20biting%20and%20scavenging.%20Our%20top%20picks%20are%20basket%20muzzles%2C%20sleeves%20for%20vet%20and%20groomer%20visits%2C%20and%20short-snout%20designs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22frea%40insider.com%20(Francesca%20Rea%2CShoshi%20Parks%2CSorin%20McKnight)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-muzzle%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20warns%20netas%20from%20Kerala%20against%20speaking%20out%20of%20turn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740781046000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118637960%2Cimgsize-1876203.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcongress-warns-netas-from-kerala-against-speaking-out-of-turn%2Farticl