20with%20an%20AV%20(audio%2Fvideo)%20receiver.%20Soundbar%20systems%20are%20the%20most%20convenient%20since%20they%20tend%20to%20take%20up%20less%20space.%20However%2C%20large%20multi-speaker%20configurations%20with%20a%20separate%20receiver%20offer%20the%20best%20performance%20with%20more%20detailed%20audio%20and%20beefier%20low%20frequencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20buying%20a%20surround%20sound%20system%2C%20you%20should%20also%20note%20the%20number%20of%20speaker%20channels%20it%20supports.%20Systems%20are%20listed%20with%20a%20string%20of%20two%20to%20three%20numbers%2C%20like%205.1%20or%205.1.4.%20The%20first%20number%20refers%20to%20the%20number%20of%20ear-level%20speakers%2C%20the%20second%20number%20refers%20to%20the%20number%20of%20dedicated%20subwoofers%2C%20and%20the%20third%20number%20refers%20to%20the%20number%20of%20overhead%20channels%20supported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20been%20reviewing%20home%20theater%20gear%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20I've%20used%20that%20experience%20to%20select%20the%20best%20surround%20systems%20for%20different%20needs.%20For%20most%20people%2C%20I%20recommend%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74754-20%26h%3Dd156a50779003688521248cf49ba91c2c6e51ac444ad0b2999670dae7b3b5047%26postID%3D67c21603b6f897a2203f3acb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-surround-sound-systems%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0BVWCDMNN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESamsung%20Q990C%20soundbar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20Dolby%20Atmos%20setup%20comes%20with%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20create%20an%20immersive%20experience%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20rooms.%20But%20buyers%20who%20have%20the%20space%20and%20budget%20for%20full-sized%20speakers%20should%20consider%20the%20higher-end%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliate