Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20testing%20material%20includes%20Blu-ray%20disc%20content%20with%20lossless%20audio%2C%20high-resolution%20music%20tracks%2C%20and%20compressed%20streaming%20audio%2C%20so%20we%20can%20hear%20how%20a%20surround%20sound%20system%20handles%20different%20levels%20of%20quality.%20Small%20and%20medium-sized%20systems%20are%20tested%20in%20a%20medium-sized%20home%20office%20space%2C%20while%20bigger%20systems%20with%20full-sized%20speakers%20are%20evaluated%20in%20a%20larger%20living%20room.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcdd0a8e-4ea3-4d18-81a7-3df97a90f7da%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESurround%20sound%20system%20FAQs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Denon%20A%2FV%20receiver%20in%20a%20TV%20console%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f46a8745edd800183b4233%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20AV%20receiver%2C%20like%20the%20Denon%20model%20pictured%20above%2C%20is%20required%20to%20power%20passive%20speaker%20systems.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20surround%20sound%20speaker%20channels%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20surround%20sound%20system%20you'll%20often%20see%20a%20string%20of%20two%20to%20three%20numbers%20separated%20by%20decimal%20points%20listed%20somewhere%20in%20the%20product%20description.%20For%20example%2C%20many%20systems%20are%20listed%20as%20being%205.1%20or%205.1.4%20setups.%20This%20string%20of%20numbers%20refers%20to%20how%20many%20speaker%20channels%20the%20system%20supports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20number%20designates%20the%20amount%20of%20standard%20ear-level%20speaker%20channels%20provided.%20The%20second%20number%20indicates%20how%20many%20subwoofers%20are%20supported%20for%20dedicated%20bass.%20The%20final%20number%20describes%20how%20many%20height%20speaker%20channels%20are%20supported%20for%20Dolby%20Atmos%20overhead%20audio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20surround%20sound%20systems%20are%20available%20in%20various%20channel%20configurations.%20Generally%2C%20the%20more%20speaker%20channels%20you%20get%2C%20the%20more%20enveloping%20and%20immersive%20the%20surround%20sound%20effect%20will%20be%20since%20audio%20can%20come%20from%20more%20directions.%20The%20most%20traditional%20setup%20is%20a%20standard%205.1%20configuration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%205.1-channel%20system%2C%20you%20get%20front%20left%2C%20front%20right%2C%20center%2C%20surround%20left%2C%20surround%20right%2C%20and%20subwoofer%20speakers%20at%20ear%20level.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20Dolby%20Atmos-capable%20system%2C%20like%20a%205.1.4%20setup%2C%20you%20get%20the%20same%20ear-level%20channels%20along%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20front%20left%20height%2C%20front%20right%20height%2C%20surround%20left%20height%2C%20and%20surround%20right%20height%20speakers.%20These%20speakers%20are%20either%20positioned%20on%20your%20ceiling%20or%20angled%20from%20the%20ground%20to%20bounce%20audio%20off%20your%20ceiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurround%20sound%20systems%20can%20start%20at%20three%20channels%2C%20and%20most%20consumer%20options%20max%20out%20at%20around%2011%20ear-level%20speakers%20and%20four%20height-level%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20Dolby%20Atmos%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDolby%20Atmos%20is%20an%20immersive%20surround%20sound%20format%20supported%20on%20many%20modern%20audio%20systems.%20It%20uses%20object-based%20audio%20mixing%2C%20which%20allows%20sound%20designers%20to%20create%20soundtracks%20with%20individual%20audio%20elements%2C%20like%20a%20buzzing%20bee%20or%20flying%20helicopter%2C%20that%20can%20be%20freely%20moved%20around%20a%20virtual%20environment.%20A%20Dolby%20Atmos%20sound%20system%20processes%20this%20location%20data%20and%20maps%20those%20locations%20to%20best%20match%20whatever%20speaker%20setup%20you%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20whether%20you%20have%20a%205.1.2%20or%2011.1.4%20speaker%20setup%2C%20a%20Dolby%20Atmos%20audio%20track%20can%20scale%20to%20match%20the%20location%20and%20number%20of%20speakers%20in%20your%20room.%20Atmos%20mixing%20also%20allows%20audio%20designers%20to%20expand%20upon%20traditional%20surround%20sound%20with%20effects%20above%20your%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDolby%20Atmos%20height%20effects%20are%20best%20realized%20by%20actual%20in-%20or%20on-ceiling%20speakers%2C%20but%20this%20type%20of%20configuration%20is%20complicated%20to%20set%20up.%20As%20an%20alternative%2C%20many%20soundbars%20and%20speakers%20use%20up-firing%20audio%20drivers%20instead.%20Up-firing%20drivers%20are%20built%20into%20ear-level%20speakers%20and%20angled%20in%20a%20specific%20way%20to%20bounce%20audio%20off%20your%20ceiling.%20This%20simulates%20the%20effect%20of%20sounds%20coming%20from%20above%20your%20head.%20The%20performance%20of%20up-firing%20speakers%20is%20affected%20by%20the%20size%20and%20shape%20of%20your%20room.%20For%20the%20best%20performance%2C%20Dolby%20suggests%20using%20a%20room%20with%20a%20flat%20ceiling%20between%207.5%20and%2012%20feet%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20details%20about%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20visit%20our%20full%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-dolby-atmos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Dolby%20Atmos%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%26quot%3B%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20you%20need%20an%20AV%20receiver%20for%20surround%20sound%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20types%20of%20surround%20sound%20systems%20sold%20today%3A%20soundbar%20setups%20and%20multi-speaker%20setups.%20Soundbar%20systems%20do%20not%20require%20a%20separate%20AV%20receiver%2C%20but%20traditional%20multi-speaker%20systems%20do.%20These%20configurations%20use%20passive%20speakers%20that%20need%20to%20be%20hooked%20up%20to%20a%20receiver%20for%20amplification%20and%20audio%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AV%20receiver%20provides%20power%20to%20your%20speakers%20and%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20connection%20hub%20for%20your%20media%20devices.%20Many%20receivers%20have%20multiple%20HDMI%20passthrough%20ports%20and%20an%20HDMI%20ARC%20(audio%20return%20channel)%20port.%20You%20can%20connect%20external%20components%20like%20a%20Blu-ray%20player%2C%20streaming%20player%2C%20or%20gaming%20console%20to%20your%20receiver's%20HDMI%20passthrough%20ports%20and%20then%20feed%20their%20signals%20to%20your%20TV%20through%20the%20HDMI%20ARC%20port.%20HDMI%20ARC%20also%20passes%20audio%20from%20your%20TV%20to%20the%20receiver.%20Many%20AV%20receivers%20also%20include%20wireless%20connectivity%20for%20music%20streaming%20via%20Bluetooth%20or%20WiFi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReceivers%20can%20power%20multiple%20speakers%20and%20the%20number%20they%20can%20support%20is%20designated%20by%20their%20channel%20specification.%20Common%20surround%20sound%20AV%20receiver%20options%20include%205.1-%2C%207.1-%2C%209.1-%2C%20and%2011.1-channel%20models.%20Some%20receivers%20support%20multiple%20subwoofers%20as%20well%2C%20which%20would%20be%20designated%20by%20a%20.2%20or%20.4%20as%20the%20second%20number.%20Generally%20speaking%2C%20the%20more%20channels%2Fspeakers%20a%20receiver%20supports%2C%20the%20more%20expensive%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20virtual%20surround%20sound%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EPhysical%20rear%20speakers%20provide%20the%20best%20surround%20sound%20quality%2C%20but%20some%20brands%20sell%20stand-alone%20soundbar%20models%20that%20support%20virtual%20surround%20sound%20without%20actual%20rear%20speakers.%20Virtual%20surround%20sound%20relies%20on%20software%20and%20psychoacoustics%20to%20simulate%20the%20effect%20of%20rear%20audio%20through%20specific%20adjustments%20in%20sound%20frequencies%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20levels.%20Some%20soundbars%20with%20virtual%20surround%20sound%20also%20rely%20on%20side-firing%20audio%20drivers%20that%20can%20bounce%20effects%20off%20your%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20virtual%20surround%20sound%20systems%20can%20provide%20a%20more%20immersive%20experience%20than%20standard%20two-channel%20stereo%20systems%2C%20we've%20yet%20to%20come%20across%20any%20stand-alone%20soundbars%20that%20can%20effectively%20mimic%20the%20sound%20of%20actual%20rear%20speakers.%20These%20models%20create%20a%20wider%20sound%20field%2C%20and%20they're%20great%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20save%20space%2C%20but%20we%20recommend%20sticking%20with%20a%20system%20that%20has%20physical%20rear%20speakers%20to%20get%20the%20best%20surround%20sound%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20speaker%20recommendations%20with%20virtual%20surround%20sound%2C%20check%20out%20our%20guides%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-soundbar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20soundbars%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-budget-soundbars%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20budget%20soundbars%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimage%2F-764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-surround-sound-systems%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740777722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c21979b8b41a9673f95bcf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-surround-sound-systems%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20surround%20sound%20systems%20create%20a%20rich%20listening%20environment.%20Our%20picks%20include%20soundbar%20and%20multi-speaker%20options%20across%20budgets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22scohen%40insider.com