20so%20that%20the%20bullets%20stop%20flying%2C%20and%20no%20more%20lives%20are%20lost.%20I%20am%20here%2C%20and%20I%20want%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20but%20clearly%20you%20don't%20want%20a%20ceasefire%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20an%20accusatory%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20hit%20back%20again%20asking%20Trump%20to%20%26quot%3Bask%20your%20predecessors%20what%20they%20have%20to%20say%20about%20the%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20which%20Trump%20immediately%20said%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20guy%20named%20Biden%2C%20who%20was%20not%20a%20smart%20person%26quot%3B%20insulting%20the%20former%20US%20President%20-%20something%20he%20had%20done%20during%20campaign%20rallies%2C%20but%20perhaps%20never%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office.%20The%20remark%20will%20almost%20certainly%20widen%20the%20fissure%20between%20the%20Republicans%20and%20the%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that%20was%20your%20President%26quot%3B%2C%20exclaimed%20Zelensky%2C%20himself%20a%20bit%20shocked%20at%20Trump's%20outburst%20on%20Biden.%20Trump%20continued%20speaking%20over%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BI%20gave%20you%20javelins%20(a%20man-portable%20anti-tank%20system).%20Obama%20gave%20you%20sheets%20(to%20cover%20bodies).%20You%20have%20got%20to%20be%20more%20thankful%20to%20the%20person%20who%20actually%20helped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20me%20be%20very%20straight%20with%20you%20-%20you%20do%20not%20have%20the%20cards.%20With%20us%2C%20you%20have%20the%20cards%2C%20and%20without%20us%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20any%20cards%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20said%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20argument%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%3Ecacophony%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3Epress%20filled%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20high-decibel%20meeting%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20immediately%20shared%20a%20message%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20Truth%20Social%2C%20in%20which%20he%20wrote%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20have%20determined%20that%20President%20Zelenskyy%20is%20not%20ready%20for%20Peace%20if%20America%20is%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2F114082877976878390%2Fembed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20disrespected%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20in%20its%20cherished%20Oval%20Office.%20He%20can%20come%20back%20when%20he%20is%20ready%20for%20Peace%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Trump%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20this%20ugly%20meeting%2C%20the%20hope%20for%20peace%20in%20Ukraine%20now%20seems%20indefinitely%20delayed%20as%20President%20Zelensky%20left%20without%20signing%20the%20crucial%20deal%20which%20would%20be%20the%20first%20step%20to%20a%20ceasefire.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740773520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F4nh5ug5g_trump-zelensky-argument-trump-zelensky-meeting-afp_625x300_28_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmake-a-deal-or-we-are-out-trump-and-zelensky-argue-in-oval-office-7818820%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Minutes%20into%20the%20meeting%20between%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Ukraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%2C%20a%20verbal%20duel%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20two%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20buy%20Blackpink%20tickets%3A%20World%20tour%20concert%20dates%20and%20prices%20compared%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfi