%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20hit%20back%2C%20asking%20how%20Vance%20would%20know%20about%20Ukraine's%20problems%20without%20visiting%20the%20country.%20The%20Ukrainian%20president%20said%20everybody%20has%20problems%20during%20a%20war%20and%20that%20the%20US%20will%20also%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20it%20in%20the%20future%26quot%3B%2C%20prompting%20a%20sharp%20rebuke%20from%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20know%20that%2C%20don't%20tell%20us%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20feel.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20solve%20a%20problem.%20You%20are%20in%20no%20position%20to%20dictate%20that...%20You%20have%20allowed%20yourself%20to%20be%20in%20a%20very%20bad%20position.%20You%20don't%20have%20the%20cards%20right%20now%2C%20with%20us%20you%20start%20having%20cards.%20You%20are%20gambling%20with%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20people.%20You%20are%20gambling%20with%20world%20war%20three.%20And%20what%20you%20are%20doing%20is%20very%20disrespectful%20to%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20staying%20in%20our%20country%2C%20staying%20strong%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20the%20war.%20And%20we%20are%20thankful%20(to%20the%20US).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20possible%20reference%20to%20his%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Trump%20then%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20gave%20you%2C%20through%20a%20stupid%20president%2C%20%24350%20billion.%20We%20gave%20you%20military%20equipment.%20If%20you%20didn't%20have%20our%20military%20equipment%2C%20this%20war%20would%20have%20been%20over%20in%20two%20weeks.%20Your%20country%20is%20in%20big%20trouble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStruggling%20to%20get%20a%20word%20in%20edgeways%2C%20Zelensky%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20invited%20me%20here...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Proudest%20Legacy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriday%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Trump%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20remembered%20as%20a%20peacemaker.%20Even%20during%20his%20inauguration%20on%20January%2020%2C%20the%20US%20President%20pointed%20to%20the%20ceasefire%20deal%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20proudest%20legacy%20will%20be%20that%20of%20a%20peacemaker%20and%20unifier.%20That's%20what%20I%20want%20to%20be%20-%20a%20peacemaker%20and%20a%20unifier.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20pleased%20to%20say%20that%2C%20as%20of%20yesterday%2C%20one%20day%20before%20I%20assumed%20office%2C%20the%20hostages%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20are%20coming%20back%20home%20to%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20have%2C%20however%2C%20accused%20Trump%20of%20favouring%20Russia%20and%20trying%20to%20extract%20concessions%20from%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740768600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fssfgs7ag_trumpzelensky-reuters_625x300_28_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-minerals-deal-hope-im-going-to-be-remembered-as-a-peacemaker-donald-trump-at-volodymyr-zelensky-meet-7819086%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20he%20called%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictator%26quot%3B%20and%20walked%20back%20the%20statement%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Friday%20said%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20discussions%20with%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%20because%20he%20hopes%20to%20be%20remembered%20as%20a%20peacemaker.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-ukraine-war-minerals-deal-hope-im-going-to-be-remembered-as-a-peacemaker-donald-trump-at-volodymyr-zelensky-meet-7819086%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Everything%20They%20Say%20Not%20Gospel%20Truth%3A%20Court%20On%20Criminal%20Complaints%20By%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20that%20in%20criminal%20cases%2C%20including%20sexual%20crimes%2C%20there%20is%20no%20presumption%20that%20everything%20the%20complainant%20woman%20says%20is%20%26quot%3Bgospel%20truth%26quot%3B%20as%20nowadays%20there%20is%20a%20tendency%20to%20implicate%20innocent%20people%20in%20such%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observations%20by%20Justice%20P%20V%20Kunhikrishnan%20came%20while%20granting%20anticipatory%20bail%20to%20a%20man%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20a%20former%20woman%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%20that%20in%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20police%20did%20not%20investigate%20the%20accused's%20initial%20complaint%20that%20the%20woman%20had%20verbally%20abused%20and%20made%20threats%20against%20him%20after%20he%20fired%20her%20for%20not%20working%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20investigation%20of%20a%20criminal%20case%20means%20probing%20the%20case%20of%20the%20complainant%20and%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20cannot%20be%20any%20unilateral%20investigation%20of%20the%20case%20put%20up%20by%20the%20complainant%20alone.%20Merely%20because%20the%20de%20facto%20complainant%20is%20a%20lady%2C%20there%20is%20no%20presumption%20that%2C%20in%20all%20cases%2C%20her%20versions%20are%20gospel%20truth%2C%20and%20the%20police%20can%20proceed%20based%20on%20her%20statement%20without%20considering%20the%20case%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNowadays%2C%20there%20is%20a%20tendency%20to%20implicate%20innocent%20people%20in%20criminal%20cases%20with%20serious%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20its%20order%20dated%20February%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20said%20that%20if%20the%20police%20find%20that%20the%20allegations%20of%20such%20women%20against%20men%20are%20false%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20can%20very%20well%20take%20action%20against%20the%20complainants%20also%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20law%20permits%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20the%20damages%20caused%20to%20a%20citizen%20because%20of%20false%20implication%20cannot%20be%20compensated%20by%20payment%20of%20money%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20integrity%2C%20position%20in%20the%20society%2C%20reputation%2C%20etc%2C%20can%20be%20ruined%20by%20a%20single%20false%20complaint.%20The%20police%20authorities%20should%20be%20alert%20and%20vigilant%2C%20to%20find%20the%20truth%20in%20criminal%20cases%20during%20the%20investigation%20stage%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%2C%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20police%20to%20separate%20the%20chaff%20from%20the%20grain%2C%20before%20submitting%20final%20reports%20in%20criminal%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20woman%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%2C%20who%20was%20the%20manager%20of%20a%20company%20where%20she%20worked%2C%20grabbed%20her%20arms%20with%20sexual%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20accused%20had%20complained%20to%20the%20police%20about%20the%20woman's%20verbal%20abuse%20and%20threats%20and%20also%20gave%20a%20pen%20drive%20containing%20an%20audio%20recording%20of%20what%20she%20had%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20it%20was%20a%20fit%20case%20where%20the%20investigating%20officer%20(IO)%20ought%20to%20have%20probed%20the%20accused's%20complaint%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20directed%20the%20accused%20to%20produce%20the%20pen%20drive%20before%20the%20IO%20and%20ordered%20the%20officer%20to%20investigate%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...if%20the%20de%20facto%20complainant%20(woman)%20is%20found%20to%20have%20submitted%20a%20false%20case%20against%20the%20petitioner%20(accused)%2C%20appropriate%20action%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%2C%20should%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20directed%20the%20accused%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20IO%20for%20interrogation%20and%20said%20that%20if%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20then%20he%20shall%20be%20released%20on%20bail%20on%20executing%20a%20bond%20for%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20with%20two%20solvent%20sureties%20each%20for%20the%20like%20sum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20bail%20conditions%20included%20appearing%20before%20the%20IO%20as%20and%20when%20required%2C%20cooperating%20with%20the%20probe%20and%20not%20to%20influence%20or%20intimidate%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740767760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feverything-they-say-not-gospel-truth-kerala-high-court-on-criminal-complaints-by-women-7819087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kerala%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20that%20in%20criminal%20cases%2C%20including%20sexual%20crimes%2C%20there%20is%20no%20presumption%20that%20everything%20the%20complainant%20woman%20says%20is%20%26quot%3Bgospel%20truth%26quot%3B%20as%20nowadays%20there%20is%20a%20tendency%20to%20implicate%20innocent%20people%20in%20such%20matters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feverything-they-say-not-gospel-truth-kerala-high-court-on-criminal-complaints-by-women-7819087%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jose%20Mourinho%20suing%20rival%20club%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20racism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740767760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F02%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-mourinho-jose_6842562.jpg%3F20250228184514%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.