Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-to-india-with-family-kids-study-abroad-experience-delhi-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etour%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Intrepid%20Travel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20we%20arrived%20at%20the%20Desert%20Resort%20in%20Mandala%2C%20I%20realized%20I'd%20failed%20to%20notice%20the%20fine%20print%20that%20WiFi%20would%20be%20extremely%20limited%20at%20this%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f39bcdcf-3622-4d8c-93c8-6be8e0052e35%5C%22%3ESurprisingly%2C%20I%20adjusted%20much%20more%20quickly%20than%20I%20expected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jamie%20relaxing%20at%20a%20resort%20in%20india%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bf2fe6b8b41a9673f9043c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInitially%2C%20I%20panicked%20a%20little%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20internet%20connection.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Davis%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20instinct%20was%20to%20panic%20when%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20resort%20intentionally%20doesn't%20provide%20WiFi%20in%20any%20of%20its%20guest%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20we%20were%20only%20there%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20I%20was%20convinced%20my%20stay%20would%20be%20stressful%20and%20difficult%20without%2024%2F7%20access%20to%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20arriving%2C%20I%20learned%20there%20were%20a%20few%20small%20areas%20with%20WiFi%20on%20the%20property%20and%20quickly%20scoped%20one%20of%20them%20out%20to%20answer%20a%20few%20emails%20that%20couldn't%20wait.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20instead%20of%20hunkering%20down%20to%20do%20more%20work%20like%20I%20might%20have%20otherwise%2C%20I%20put%20my%20computer%20back%20in%20my%20room%20and%20explored%20the%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20surprise%2C%20my%20stress%20about%20the%20WiFi%20melted%20away%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%