States%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20negotiations%20of%20a%20possible%20truce%20in%20the%20years-long%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20comes%20amid%20heightened%20tensions%20after%20President%20Trump%20earlier%20called%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictator%26quot%3B%20and%20blamed%20him%20for%20%26quot%3Bstarting%20the%20war%26quot%3B%20with%20Russia.%20He%20however%2C%20took%20back%20his%20words%20a%20day%20before%20the%20meeting%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bdid%20I%20really%20say%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20commended%20Zelensky%20for%20his%20bravery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20talks%20began%2C%20Ukraine's%20President%20Zelensky%20urged%20Donald%20Trump%20that%20during%20peace%20talks%20%26quot%3Bthere%20should%20be%20no%20compromises%20with%20a%20killer%20on%20our%20territory%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20an%20apparent%20reference%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20but%20President%20Trump%20made%20it%20amply%20clear%20that%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20will%20have%20to%20make%20compromises%20in%20a%20truce%20with%20Russia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20meeting%20began%2C%20President%20Zelensky%20had%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20President%20Trump%20is%20on%20our%20side%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20told%20the%20US%20President%20that%20the%20US%20protecting%20Ukraine%20from%20Russian%20threats%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20crucial%26quot%3B%20for%20peacekeepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20truce%20with%20Russia%20is%20fairly%20close%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20deal%20allowing%20US%20access%20to%20Ukraine's%20natural%20resources%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20fair%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESigning%20of%20a%20resources%20deal%20will%20give%20the%20United%20States%20access%20to%20rare-earth%20and%20other%20critical%20minerals%20as%20part%20of%20an%20overall%20plan%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20recover%20after%20a%20truce%20in%20the%20war%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20MINERALS%20DEAL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agenda%20of%20today's%20meeting%20primarily%20focuses%20on%20this%20minerals%20deal%20for%20the%20United%20States%20in%20return%20for%20Washington's%20assurance%20of%20providing%20Kyiv%20with%20the%20security%20it%20needs%20against%20Russia.%20The%20deal%20is%20important%20as%20it%20forms%20the%20foundation%20of%20future%20talks%20on%20finding%20a%20peace%20deal%20for%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20on%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2C%20which%20shares%20the%20maximum%20burden%20among%20all%20NATO%20allies%20to%20provide%20a%20security%20cover%20across%20Europe%2C%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20significantly%20enhance%20their%20share%20of%20the%20military%20and%20financial%20burden.%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20threatened%20that%20he%20will%20even%20consider%20withdrawing%20from%20providing%20security%20to%20Europe%20should%20everyone%20not%20contribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20has%20said%20in%20the%20past%20that%20he%20does%20not%20see%20any%20benefit%20for%20Washington%20in%20staying%20involved%20in%20Ukraine%20since%20%26quot%3BEurope%20has%20a%20guarantee%20on%20what%20it%20has%20spent%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20the%20US%20does%20not%26quot%3B.%20Amid%20all%20this%2C%20European%20leaders%2C%20with%20President%20Zelensky's%20willingness%2C%20suggested%20that%20Ukraine%20do%20a%20minerals%20deal%20with%20Washington%2C%20so%20that%20US%20also%20has%20a%20way%20of%20getting%20back%20what%20it%20is%20spending%20in%20Ukraine%20-%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20security%20as%20well%20as%20in%20helping%20rebuild%20Ukraine%20after%20the%20war.%20European%20leaders%20believe%20that%20this%20will%20keep%20the%20US%20invested%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20automatically%20providing%20for%20Kyiv's%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20EUROPE%20SAYS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20France's%20President%20Emmanuel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-meeting-donald-trump-frances-emmanuel-macron-reveals-endgame-in-ukraine-war-7794308%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMacron%20had%20met%20President%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Washington%20DC.%20He%20was%20representing%20the%20European%20Union%20in%20that%20meeting.%20After%20the%20meeting%2C%20which%20primarily%20focused%20on%20a%20peace%20deal%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20President%20Macron%20revealed%20the%20endgame%20to%20finding%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%20the%20sequence%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%20should%20be%20as%20follows%20-%20First%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20negotiation%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Russia%20and%20then%20the%20US%20and%20Ukraine.%20President%20Trump%20has%20announced%20today%20that%20he%20is%20willing%20to%20have%20a%20short-term%20meeting%20with%20Ukraine's%20President%20Zelensky%20-%20this%20is%20super%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Macron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20truce%20could%20actually%20happen%20in%20the%20weeks%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BTruce%20has%20to%20be%20achieved%20on%20land%2C%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20at%20sea%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20(installed%20in%20Ukraine)%20-%20and%20Russia%20must%20respect%20it.%20If%20it%20doesn't%2C%20it%20will%20be%20clear%20that%20Moscow%20is%20not%20serious%20about%20a%20peace%20deal%26quot%3B%20and%20Ukraine's%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20this%20period%20of%20time%20-%20when%20the%20truce%20is%20in%20place%2C%20we%20negotiate%20-%20on%20security%20guarantees%20(by%20Moscow)%2C%20on%20land%20and%20territories%20(to%20reclaim%20or%20surrender)%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%20(to%20safeguard%20Kyiv's%20interest)%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Macron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20Washington%20%26quot%3Bwill%20secure%20a%20deal%20on%20rare%20earth%20and%20other%20critical%20minerals%26quot%3B.%20Confirming%20that%20France%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe%20will%20be%20fine%20with%20this%2C%20Mr%20Macron%20explained%20that%20such%20a%20mineral%20deal%20for%20Washington%20%26quot%3Bis%20important%2C%20because%20this%20would%20be%20the%20best%20way%20to%20guarantee%20that%20the%20US%20is%20also%20committed%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20back%20out%20of%20Ukraine's%20safety%20and%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20the%20back%20of%20these%20set%20of%20manoeuvres%2C%20with%20all%20parties%20invested%20in%20maintaining%20Ukraine's%20sovereignty%2C%20we%20will%20finally%20have%20a%20peace%20deal%2C%20he%20explained.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740764280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fod3dged8_trump-zelensky-meet-afp_625x300_28_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fzelensky-meets-trump-at-white-house-minerals-deal-on-agenda-7818399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20met%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House%20today%2C%20as%20both%20leaders%20discussed%20a%20minerals%20deal%20for%20the%20United%20States%20as%20part%20of%20negotiations%20of%20a%20possible%20truce%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'The%20Brutalist'%20feels%20deeply%20relevant%3A%20Jones%20and%20Pearce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740764028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118634720%2Cimgsize-33212.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fthe-brutalist-feels-deeply-relevant-amid-todays