hat%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20anyone%20crossing%20the%20party%20line%20and%20saying%20something%20that%20goes%20against%20the%20party.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20there%20is%20a%20controversy%20by%20the%20media%20and%20by%20the%20translation%20of%20what%20he%20said...%20I%20will%20say%20there%20is%20no%20one%20in%20the%20Kerala%20unit%20of%20the%20party%20who%20is%20pro-Left%20Democratic%20Front%20(LDF)%20or%20pro-BJP.%20Everyone%20is%20fighting%20against%20(them)%20and%20fighting%20unitedly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20message%20was%20also%20given%20by%20senior%20party%20leader%20Ramesh%20Chennithala.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20will%20be%20united%20and%20fight%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala%20as%20the%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20on%20all%20fronts.%20We%20will%20fight%20and%20a%20(Congress-led)%20United%20Democratic%20front%20will%20come%20to%20power%20in%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20leaders%20from%20Kerala%2C%20including%20Mr%20Tharoor%20and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20K%20Sudhakaran%2C%20the%20brainstorming%20meeting%20-%20which%20went%20on%20for%20nearly%20three%20hours%20-%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20General%20Secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Wayanad%20MP%20Priyanka%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20shared%20photos%20and%20videos%20from%20the%20meeting%20and%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Kerala%20will%20defeat%20both%20the%20%26quot%3Boppressive%20and%20communal%26quot%3B%20fronts%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChange%20is%20inevitable%20in%20Kerala.%20Congress%20has%20built%20the%20development%20paradigm%20and%20welfare%20model%20of%20Kerala%2C%20and%20we%20will%20do%20everything%20possible%20to%20bring%20our%20UDF%20to%20power.%20Next%20year%2C%20people%20will%20defeat%20both%20the%20oppressive%20and%20communal%20fronts%20in%20the%20state.%20We%20held%20a%20meeting%20of%20%40INCKerala%20leaders%20where%20we%20deliberated%20on%20our%20political%20strategy%20and%20the%20future%20of%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESparking%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20came%20under%20fire%20from%20some%20Congress%20leaders%20for%20praising%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20where%20he%20met%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20led%20to%20some%20positive%20outcomes%20for%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20wrote%20an%20article%20in%20an%20English%20daily%20in%20which%20he%20was%20seen%20as%20praising%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan-led%20LDF%20government%20in%20some%20sectors.%20While%20some%20in%20the%20Congress%20slammed%20the%20remarks%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Vijayan%20said%20they%20were%20proof%20of%20his%20government's%20achievements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20his%20remarks%20on%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20had%20said%20that%20he%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Balways%20speak%20in%20terms%20of%20party%20interest%26quot%3B.%20On%20the%20article%2C%20the%20MP%20said%20he%20was%20focusing%20on%20the%20startup%20sector%20in%20Kerala%2C%20the%20seeds%20for%20which%20were%20sown%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20government%20under%20Oommen%20Chandy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Kerala%2C%20I%20wrote%20this%20article%20focusing%20on%20a%20specific%20issue%20--%20the%20transformation%20of%20the%20industrial%20landscape%20through%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20startup%20sector.%20As%20a%20Congress%20worker%2C%20I%20take%20pride%20in%20acknowledging%20that%20it%20was%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Oommen%20Chandy%20who%20initiated%20this%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22