0on%20one%20of%20the%20complaints%20filed%20by%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20the%20woman%20filed%20three%20complaints%20and%20three%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIR)%20and%20changed%20her%20statements%20several%20times%2C%20even%20submitting%20applications%20seeking%20that%20the%20complaints%20filed%20by%20her%20be%20withdrawn.%20Police%20said%20her%20last%20FIR%2C%20in%20which%20she%20alleged%20she%20was%20gangraped%20by%20her%20husband's%20friends%20and%20a%20bottle%20had%20been%20inserted%20in%20her%20private%20parts%2C%20was%20found%20to%20be%20false%20and%20she%20was%20arrested%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeries%20Of%20Allegations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20last%20year%2C%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20was%20in%20a%20live-in%20relationship%20with%20Vikas%20Tyagi%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Ghaziabad's%20Kavi%20Nagar%2C%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20raped%20her%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20marrying%20her.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20pregnant%20at%20the%20time%20and%20the%20child%20had%20died%20because%20she%20was%20sexually%20assaulted%20and%20because%20Tyagi%20had%20kicked%20her%20in%20the%20stomach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20repeated%20her%20allegations%20in%20her%20first%20statement%20but%20changed%20tack%20when%20her%20statement%20was%20being%20recorded%20before%20a%20judicial%20magistrate%2C%20officials%20said.%20In%20her%20second%20statement%2C%20she%20said%20that%20the%20relationship%20was%20consensual%20and%20Tyagi%20had%20only%20beaten%20her%2C%20but%20they%20had%20come%20to%20an%20agreement%20outside%20court%20about%20that.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20she%20had%20suffered%20a%20miscarriage%20because%20she%20had%20not%20followed%20her%20doctor's%20advice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20woman%20approached%20the%20police%20again%20and%20said%20she%20had%20changed%20her%20statement%20in%20the%20June%20case%20because%20Tyagi%2C%20his%20brother-in-law%20and%20one%20of%20his%20friends%20had%20threatened%20to%20kill%20her%20if%20she%20did%20not%20do%20so.%20A%20police%20statement%20said%20that%20she%20submitted%20an%20application%20later%20the%20same%20month%20stating%20that%20she%20had%20married%20Tyagi%20and%20requested%20that%20action%20be%20stopped%20on%20her%20earlier%20complaint.%20She%20also%20uploaded%20a%20video%20saying%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHusband%20Jailed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20months%20later%2C%20in%20January%2C%20she%20submitted%20complaints%20and%20filed%20an%20FIR%20stating%20that%20Tyagi%20and%20her%20mother%20had%20got%20the%20wedding%20conducted%20in%20an%20incomplete%20manner%20and%20he%20had%20raped%20her%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20marriage.%20She%20also%20said%20Tyagi%20had%20thrashed%20her%20and%20tried%20to%20set%20her%20ablaze%20by%20pouring%20alcohol%20on%20her%20and%2C%20later%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20claimed%20she%20was%20gangraped%20by%20him%20and%20two%20of%20his%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20investigations%20revealed%20that%20the%20gang-rape%20accusations%20were%20false%2C%20her%20medical%20report%20showed%20evidence%20of%20burn%20injuries.%20Tyagi%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%2017%20and%20is%20in%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20woman%20made%20her%20most%20serious%20allegation%20yet%2C%20claiming%20that%20three%20of%20Tyagi's%20friends%20kidnapped%20her%20when%20she%20was%20on%20her%20way%20to%20the%20market%2C%20made%20her%20numb%20by%20injecting%20some%20substance%20into%20her%20and%20took%20turns%20raping%20her.%20She%20also%20alleged%20that%20they%20put%20some%20chemical%20on%20her%20neck%2C%20inserted%20a%20bottle%20in%20her%20private%20parts%20and%20threw%20her%20on%20a%20garbage%20heap%20near%20Mehrauli%20Gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20Monday.%20When%20police%20checked%20the%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20however%2C%20they%20found%20that%20she%20had%20left%20her%20house%20around%208.30%20pm%2C%20sat%20in%20a%20car%20later%20and%20was%20dropped%20home%20at%2010.19%20pm.%20She%20was%20seen%20walking%20normally%20to%20her%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20records%20and%20location%20details%20of%20Tyagi's%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20accused%20by%20the%20woman%2C%20revealed%20that%20they%20were%20not%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20alleged%20crime.%20During%20her%20medical%20checkup%2C%20the%20chemical%20that%20she%20claimed%20was%20poured%20on%20her%20neck%20also%20appeared%20to%20have%20been%20applied%20with%20cotton.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20Of%20Police%20Rajesh%20Kumar%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20received%20the%20gang-rape%20complaint%20on%20February%2025.%20When%20we%20investigated%20and%20conducted%20a%20medical%20checkup%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20FIR%20against%20her%20husband's%20friends%20was%20false%2C%20concocted%20and%20filed%20because%20of%20some%20motive.%20She%20has%20filed%20complaints%20and%20applications%20before%20and%20her%20husband%20is%20in%20jail%20in%20connection%20with%20one%20of%20them...%20The%20woman%20has%20now%20been%20arrested.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20the%20possible%20motive%20was%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20woman%20has%20been%20living%20in%20Tyagi's%20flat%20since%20their%20relationship%20began.%20The%20motive%20could%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20flat.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Vipin%20Tomar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740757800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fb5c78o38_woman-arrested-for-false-gangrape-complaint_625x300_28_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghaziabad-woman-alleges-brutal-gang-rape-arrested-after-claims-found-false-7816876%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20Ghaziabad%20for%20repeatedly%20levelling%20allegations%20of%20rape%2C%20gang-rape%20and%20kidnapping%20against%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20her%20live-in%20partner%2C%20and%20his%20friends.%20Police%20said%20her%20latest%20allegation%20was%20found%20to%20be%20false%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fghaziabad-woman-alleges-brutal-gang-rape-arrested-after-claims-found-false-7816876%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20First%20Clinics%20For%20Transgenders%20Close%20After%20USAID%20Freeze%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20first%20three%20clinics%20for%20the%20transgender%20community%20closed%20last%20month%20following%20a%20stop-work%20order%20from%20the%20US%20Agency%20for%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%20that%20funded%20them%2C%20disrupting%20services%20for%20nearly%205%2C000%20people%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20quoting%20two%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20ordered%20a%2090-day%20pause%20on%20all%20foreign%20aid%20in%20January%20pending%20a%20review%20to%20ensure%20all%20projects%20funded%20with%20US%20taxpayer%20money%20are%20aligned%20with%20his%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20First%26quot%3B%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20criticised%20what%20he%20called%20USAID%20spending%20%2421%20million%20on%20%26quot%3Bvoter%20turnout%26quot%3B%20in%20India.%20The%20Centre%20said%20last%20week%20it%20was%20investigating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20main%20losers%20following%20the%20fund%20freeze%20have%20been%20three%20Mitr%20(friend)%20Clinics%20in%20India%20that%20are%20run%20mostly%20by%20doctors%2C%20counsellors%20and%20other%20workers%20from%20the%20transgender%20community%20and%20that%20serve%20up%20to%205%2C000%20people%2C%20said%20the%20sources.%20Both%20declined%20to%20be%20named%2C%20citing%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20ally%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Republican%20Senator%20John%20Kennedy%20have%20both%20criticised%20the%20transgender%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20American%20tax%20dollars%20were%20funding%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20on%20X%20on%20Friday%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20about%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20first%20of%20the%20Mitr%20clinics%2C%20launched%20in%20the%20southern%20Indian%20city%20of%20Hyderabad%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20clinics%20are%20located%20in%20the%20cities%20of%20Kalyan%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20provided%20services%20including%20guidance%20and%20medication%20on%20hormone%20therapy%2C%20counselling%20on%20mental%20health%20as%20well%20as%20on%20HIV%20and%20other%20sexually%20transmitted%20diseases%2C%20and%20legal%20aid%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20general%20medical%20care%2C%20a%20website%20for%20the%20three%20clinics%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20them%20needed%20up%20to%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20(%2434%2C338)%20a%20year%20to%20run%20and%20employed%20about%20eight%20people%2C%20said%20one%20of%20the%20sources%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20were%20looking%20for%20alternate%20sources%20of%20funding%2C%20public%20or%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganisers%20of%20the%20clinics%2C%20however%2C%20have%20got%20a%20waiver%20from%20USAID%20to%20keep%20running%20certain%20life-saving%20activities%2C%20including%20providing%20antiretroviral%20medication%20to%20HIV-infected%20people%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%2010%25%20of%20all%20clinic%20clients%20are%20infected%20by%20HIV%2C%20one%20of%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20some%20really%20good%20work%20at%20Mitr%20Clinics%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20of%20the%20sources%2C%20a%20doctor.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20proud%20of%20what%20we%20achieved%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%