t%20we%20are%20currently%20witnessing%20about%20Team%20India's%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%20venue%20advantage%E2%80%9D%20in%20Dubai%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20let's%20get%20one%20thing%20out%20of%20the%20way%3A%20there%20can%20be%20no%20commercially%20successful%20global%20cricket%20tournament%2C%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20without%20the%20Indian%20team.%20Viewership%2C%20sponsorship%20revenue%20and%20overall%20interest%20in%20the%20tournament%20would%20nose-dive%20if%20India%20is%20not%20playing.%20Just%20wait%20for%20the%20viewership%20figures%20of%20the%20next%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20between%20Australia%20and%20South%20Africa%20to%20be%20released%20(if%20they%20ever%20are)%20and%20compare%20that%20with%20the%20two%20previous%20finals%20that%20have%20featured%20India.%20You%20will%20have%20your%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Questions%20To%20Ask%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20knows%20anything%20about%20cricket%20will%20agree%20that%20if%20a%20team%20is%20stationed%20at%20one%20venue%20through%20an%20entire%20multi-nation%20tournament%2C%20they%20are%20bound%20to%20have%20venue%20advantage.%20There's%20no%20denying%20that.%20They%20can%20not%20only%20adjust%20to%20the%20conditions%20once%20and%20for%20all%2C%20knowing%20well%20where%20they%20will%20be%20playing%20the%20knockout%20games%20if%20they%20reach%20that%20stage%2C%20but%20they%20also%20don't%20have%20to%20tinker%20too%20much%20with%20their%20playing%20XI%20once%20the%20best%20combination%20has%20been%20found.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20travel%20fatigue%20or%20over-the-top%20logistical%20planning%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20ask%20yourself%20two%20questions.%20One%2C%20whose%20fault%20is%20that%3F%20Can%20Rohit%20Sharma%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20based%20only%20in%20Dubai%20for%20their%20entire%20campaign%3F%20Surely%20not.%20And%20two%2C%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20Team%20India%20doing%20so%20well%2C%20having%20secured%20a%20semi-final%20berth%20with%20a%20game%20in%20hand%2C%20only%20that%20they%20are%20playing%20all%20their%20matches%20at%20the%20same%20venue%3F%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20summarily%20dismiss%20the%20efforts%20being%20put%20in%20by%20the%20players%20and%20the%20support%20staff%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETeam%20India's%20'Enviable'%20Position%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20look%20at%20how%20and%20why%20Team%20India%20found%20itself%20in%20this%20%E2%80%9Cenviable%E2%80%9D%20position%20at%20the%20ongoing%20Champions%20Trophy.%20The%20only%20reason%20India%20are%20playing%20all%20their%20matches%20in%20Dubai%20is%20because%20there%20is%20absolutely%20no%20chance%20whatsoever%20that%20the%20team%20would%20have%20been%20given%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20for%20anything.%20If%20the%20captain's%20meet%20and%20photoshoot%20had%20not%20been%20cancelled%20due%20to%20logistical%20reasons%2C%20perhaps%20Rohit%20Sharma%20would%20not%20have%20been%20given%20clearance%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20that%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20let's%20go%20back%20to%20the%20genesis%E2%80%94back%20to%202021%E2%80%94when%20the%20ICC%20awarded%20hosting%20rights%20to%20Pakistan.%20It%20must%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20the%20ICC%20Board%20has%20representatives%20of%20all%2012%20full%20members%2C%20including%20India%2C%20representatives%20from%20some%20associate%20countries%20and%20independent%20directors%2C%20along%20with%20office-bearers%20like%20the%20Chairman%20and%20CEO.%20There%20was%20no%20plan%20drawn%20up%20at%20that%20time%20for%20a%20hybrid%20model%20by%20anyone.%20Why%3F%20Was%20the%20BCCI%20categorically%20asked%20if%20their%20team%20would%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%3F%20Not%20that%20we%20know%20of.%20Did%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20raise%20this%20concern%20at%20the%20time%3F%20Again%2C%20not%20that%20we%20know%20of.%20Surely%20someone%20should%20have%20had%20the%20foresight%20that%20India%20wouldn't%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%3F%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20geopolitical%20expert%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20Indian%20government's%20stand%20is%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20four%20years%20down%20the%20line.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20security%20analyst%20to%20know%20that%20India%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Matter%20Of%20Foresight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20if%20that%20foresight%20had%20existed%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20ICC%2C%20along%20with%20hosts%20PCB%2C%20could%20have%20drawn-up%20a%20plan%20whereby%20India%20would%20play%20their%20matches%20at%20say%20two%20or%20even%20all%20three%20UAE%20venues%20(Dubai%2C%20Sharjah%20and%20Abu%20Dhabi)%2C%20and%20not%20just%20one.%20That%20way%2C%20no%20one%20would%20be%20able%20to%20say%20that%20India%20are%20playing%20only%20in%20one%20venue%20and%20enjoying%20the%20perks%20of%20venue%20familiarity.%20However%2C%20what%20eventually%20happened%20was%20the%20inevitable%20situation%20of%20India%20saying%20they%20could%20not%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20ICC%20feeling%20the%20pressure%20of%20an%20India-less%20tournament%20(which%20is%20just%20not%20feasible)%2C%20and%20then%2C%20a%20hurriedly%20put-together%20plan%20of%20Dubai%20being%20India's%20base%20camp.%20It%20takes%20a%20lot%20to%20get%20a%20venue%20ready%20for%20international%20matches%20of%20this%20scale.%20If%20this%20scenario%20had%20been%20pre-empted%2C%20many%20things%20could%20have%20been%20different.%20But%20it%20wasn't.%20And%20there%20were%20no%20voices%20of%20criticism%20at%20that%20time.%20They%20only%20began%20once%20the%20Indian%20team%20began%20to%20dominate%20proceedings%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20denying%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20other%20teams%2C%20barring%20India%2C%20might%20be%20feeling%20shortchanged.%20They%20are%20forced%20to%20travel%20from%20one%20venue%20to%20another%2C%20acclimatise%20and%20play%20their%20best%20cricket.%20The%20Indian%20team%20knew%20they%20were%20going%20to%20be%20based%20only%20and%20only%20in%20Dubai%20and%20could%20also%20select%20their%20squad%20accordingly.%20All%20of%20us%20who%20were%20scratching%20our%20heads%20a%20bit%20when%20as%20many%20as%20five%20spinners%20were%20picked%20now%20understand%20that%20it%20was%20a%20tactical%20masterstroke.%20Take%20all%20your%20spinning%20options%20and%20play%20whoever%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20most%20potent%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20opposition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Need%20For%20A%20Hybrid%20Model%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20this%20is%20not%20Team%20India%20or%20the%20current%20BCCI%20regime's%20fault.%20They%20didn't%20ask%20for%20this%20situation.%20The%20BCCI%20had%20to%20relay%20the%20official%20stance%2C%20which%20is%20that%20Indian%20players%20can't%20travel%20to%20Pakistan.%20Everyone%20knows%20what%20the%20political%20chemistry%20and%20history%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20like.%20And%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20if%20the%20government%20does%20not%20give%20the%20go-ahead%20for%20travel%20to%20a%20specific%20country%2C%20there's%20nothing%20anybody%20can%20do%20about%20it.%20Which%20is%20why%20every%20time%20the%20hosting%20rights%20for%20an%20ICC%20event%20are%20given%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20there%20must%20be%20a%20hybrid-model%20in%20place%20for%20the%20Indian%20team.%20Just%20because%20Pakistan%20travelled%20to%20India%20for%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20India%20would%20have%20reciprocated.%20If%20that's%20the%20quid-pro-quo%20that%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20had%20envisioned%20at%20that%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20complete%20fallacy.%20India%20are%20not%20%E2%80%9Cpicking%20and%20choosing%E2%80%9D%20what%20they%20want%20to%20play%20where%2C%20as%20some%20critics%20have%20said.%20Pakistan%20is%20literally%20the%20only%20country%20India%20doesn't%20travel%20to%20for%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReputable%20former%20cricketers%20should%20be%20aware%20that%20they%20have%20the%20power%20and%20privilege%20to%20make%20headlines%20with%20their%20comments.%20It's%20not%20just%20what%20they%20say%2C%20but%20also%20when%20they%20say%20it%20that%20really%20matters.%20The%20unnecessary%20controversy%20over%20India%20playing%20only%20in%20Dubai%20might%20look%20and%20sound%20like%20a%20storm%20in%20a%20teacup%20for%20all%20neutral%20parties%2C%20but%20many%20cricket%20fans%20from%20countries%20that%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Champions%20Trophy%20might%20be%20swayed%20by%20these%20comments%3B%20they%20make%20it%20sound%20as%20if%20some%20Machiavellian%20plot%20was%20hatched%20to%20give%20India%20an%20%E2%80%9Cundeniable%20advantage%E2%80%9D%20so%20as%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20final%2C%20thereby%20ensuring%20peak%20viewership%20numbers.%20This%20wasn't%20anyone's%20%E2%80%98plan'.%20If%20anything%2C%20things%20should%20be%20planned%20much%20better%20in%20the%20future%2C%20whenever%20the%20ICC%20decides%20to%20award%20Pakistan%20hosting%20rights%20for%20any%20tournament.%20All%20this%20complaining%20also%20dents%20the%20tournament's%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Pakistan%20hosted%20an%20ICC%20event%2C%20before%20this%20one%2C%20was%20the%201996%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20But%20they%20weren't%20the%20sole%20hosts.%20That%20tournament%20was%20co-hosted%20by%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20Subcontinental%20geopolitics%20is%20not%20what%20it%20was%2029%20years%20ago.%20A%20lot%20has%20changed%20since%20then.%20It's%20time%20some%20people%20change%20their%20mindset%20too.%20If%20the%20show%20must%20go%20on%2C%20amid%20political%20tensions%2C%20petty%20finger-pointing%20will%20serve%20little%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740746700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Foh1p966_cricket_625x300_08_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchampions-trophy-yes-india-has-venue-edge-but-whose-fault-is-that-7816554%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%20because%20Pakistan%20travelled%20to%20India%20for%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20India%20would%20have%20reciprocated.%20If%20that's%20the%20quid-pro-quo%20that%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20had%20envisioned%20at%20that%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20complete%20fallacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchampions-trophy-yes-india-has-venue-edge-but-whose-fault-is-that-7816554%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lost%20for%20Centuries%3A%20How%20a%20Chennai%20Craftsman%20Brought%20Back%20a%202000-Year-Old%20Tamil%20Instrument%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20small%20Chennai%20workshop%2C%2028-year-old%20Tharun%20Sekar%20meticulously%20carves%20the%20wooden%20frame%20of%20a%20musical%20instrument%20that%20had%20nearly%20vanished%20from%20Indian%20culture.%20This%20instrument%2C%20the%20Yazh%2C%20is%20a%202000-year-old%20harp-like%20string%20instrument%20once%20favoured%20by%20Tamil%20kings%20and%20celebrated%20in%20the%20third%20Sangam-era%20literature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20centuries%2C%20it%20remained%20confined%20to%20history%20books%20and%20museum%20displays%20%E2%80%94%20until%20Tharun%20took%20on%20the%20challenge%20of%20reviving%20it.%20Founder%20of%20Uru%20Instruments%2C%20Tharun%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20revive%20and%20modernise%20lo