was%20finally%20installed%20in%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20gardens%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESpreading%20the%20love%20for%20books%20across%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20first%20library%20in%20Parimal%20Garden%20motivated%20the%20duo%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20more%20parks%20across%20Ahmedabad%20saw%20the%20arrival%20of%20mini-libraries.%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20we%20installed%20mini-libraries%20in%20four%20key%20locations%2C%20including%20Prahladnagar%20Garden%2C%20Law%20Garden%2C%20Gotila%20Garden%2C%20and%20Monte%20Carlo%20Oxygen%20Park.%20These%20public%20mini-libraries%20are%20free%20and%20accessible%20to%20all%2C%20creating%20spaces%20where%20everyone%20can%20come%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310032%2Fias-officer-himanshu-kafaltia-sets-up-libraries-in-villages-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eengage%20in%20the%20world%20of%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Om.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20libraries%20have%20become%20more%20than%20just%20places%20to%20borrow%20books%2C%20they%20have%20turned%20into%20hubs%20for%20conversation%2C%20learning%2C%20and%20community-building.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20had%20the%20idea%20of%20creating%20mini-libraries%2C%20we%20had%20no%20clear%20vision%20of%20how%20the%20community%20would%20respond%2C%E2%80%9D%20reflects%20Heet.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20support%20we%20receive%20every%20day%20is%20heartwarming.%20People%20not%20only%20visit%20the%20libraries%20but%20also%20actively%20help%20maintain%20them%20by%20rearranging%20the%20books%20or%20dusting%20once%20in%20a%20while.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2F