3EThe%20process%20was%20rigorous%2C%20requiring%20complex%20logistics%20in%20remote%20and%20restricted%20areas%2C%20often%20under%20challenging%20conditions.%20Each%20installation%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20placing%20a%20pump%20in%20a%20borewell%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20in%20water%20bodies%20full%20of%20crocodiles%20or%20down%20a%20steep%20cliff%20of%20a%20waterfall.%20It%20involved%20strategic%20planning%20to%20ensure%20water%20reached%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F383592%2Fwildlife-conservation-sharvan-patel-rajasthan-whatsapp-group-save-species-habitats%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20waterbodies%2C%20thus%20benefitting%20an%20array%20of%20species%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20omnipresent%20deer%20to%20the%20elusive%20tiger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20community%20of%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20immediate%20relief%20from%20thirst%2C%20the%20transformation%20was%20remarkable.%20Dr%20Sarita%20informs%20that%20the%20vegetation%20around%20the%20water%20bodies%20flourished%2C%20drawing%20herbivores%20who%20in%20turn%20supported%20predator%20populations%20without%20them%20needing%20to%20leave%20their%20natural%20territories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20as%20if%20nature%20had%20been%20patiently%20waiting%20for%20a%20helping%20hand%20to%20tip%20the%20scales%20back%20towards%20equilibrium!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20inspiring%20is%20the%20ripple%20effect%20these%20solar%20installations%20create%20%E2%80%94%20local%20stakeholders%20also%20benefit%20from%20this%20endeavour%2C%20as%20many%20of%20the%20water%20lines%20are%20directed%20to%20anti-poaching%20outposts%2C%20freeing%20forest%20guards%20from%20weekly%20treks%20for%20water%20and%20enabling%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20safeguarding%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20innovation%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20ecological%3B%20it%20aimed%20to%20mitigate%20human-wildlife%20conflicts%2C%20an%20ever-present%20reality%20threatening%20both%20communities%20and%20wild%20species%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Sarita%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20installing%20solar%20pumps%2C%20water%20could%20be%20provided%20consistently%20across%20various%20zones%20within%20the%20reserves%2C%20ensuring%20animals%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20wander%20into%20human%20habitats%20in%20search%20of%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-pumps-2-1740399564.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22So%20far%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20completed%20170%20solar%20water%20pump%20installations%20in%2025%20forests%20and%20wildlife%20sanctuaries%20across%20seven%20states.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-pumps-2-1740399564.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-pumps-2-1740399564-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-pumps-2-1740399564-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-pumps-2-1740399564-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fsolar-pumps-2-1740399564-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-409021%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20completed%20170%20solar%20water%20pump%20installations%20in%2025%20forests%20and%20wildlife%20sanctuaries%20across%20seven%20states.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20as%20noisy%20water%20tankers%20guzzling%20diesel%20fall%20silent%2C%20the%20skies%20above%20these%20reserves%20take%20a%20breath%2C%20relieved%20of%20carbon%20emissions.%20%E2%80%9CForest%20departments%20rejoice%20in%20reducing%20their%20reliance%20on%20costly%2C%20polluting%20methods%20and%20explore%20enhanced%20biodiversity%20management%2C%E2%80%9D%20points%20out%20Dr%20Sarita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiganth%20Nayak%2C%20the%20divisional%20forest%20officer%20(DFO)%20of%20the%20Ramnagar%20Division%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20has%20been%20working%20together%20with%20The%20Earth%20Brigade%20Foundation%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20While%20lauding%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20team%2C%20he%20mentions%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20set%20up%20solar%20pumps%20which%20fill%20up%20the%20water%20holes%20as%20well%20as%20provide%20water%20to%20the%20interior%20forest%20%3Cem%3Echowki%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20Earlier%2C%20our%20staff%20would%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20stay%20in%20a%20remote%20%3Cem%3Echowki%20%3C%2Fem%3Eduring%20the%20dry%20season.%20Things%20have%20become%20much%20easier%20after%20solar%20pump%20installations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20we%20experienced%20a%20very%20dry%20summer%20with%20no%20winter%20rains%20at%20all.%20These%20water%20holes%20helped%20a%20lot%20in%20ensuring%20wildlife%20had%20at%20least%20a%20few%20points%20in%20the%20jungle%20where%20there%20would%20be%20water%20throughout%20the%20year.%20The%20water%20hole%20ideally%20needs%20to%20be%20filled%20up%20once%20a%20week%20and%20during%20hot%20summers%20once%20in%202-3%20days.%20We%20were